ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 26th day of May, 2009, the order of the PCRA court is affirmed. See Commonwealth v. Fahy, 598 Pa. 584, 959 A.2d 312 (2008); Commonwealth v. Marshall, 596 Pa. 587, 947 A.2d 714, 720-22 (2008).
opinions.author: ORDER PER CURIAM.

attorneys: David Lee Zuckerman, Esq., Philadelphia, for Craig Murphy.
Hugh J. Burns, Esq., Amy Zapp, Esq., Philadelphia District Attorney’s Office, for Commonwealth of Pennsylvania.
